nd agents—to user success and business outcomes. \",\"twitterTitle\":\"AI-Powered Analytics \u0026 Adoption Platform | Pendo\"},\"state\":{\"deviceSize\":\"large\",\"location\":{\"pathname\":\"/\",\"path\":[\"\"],\"query\":{}},\"scrollY\":0,\"openFaqIndex\":null},\"themeId\":false,\"title\":\"Product Experience \u0026 Analytics Platform | Pendo\",\"twitterDescription\":\"Twitter Description\",\"url\":\"/\",\"blocks\":[{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/sdk:Element\",\"@version\":2,\"id\":\"builder-a886152e0e9b4d45a95af6ced61b6bc6\",\"meta\":{\"localizedTextInputs\":[\"heading\",\"subheading\",\"primaryCtaText\",\"videoAriaLabel\",\"secondaryCtaText\"],\"transformed.primaryCtaUrl\":\"localized\",\"transformed.primaryCtaOpenModal\":\"localized\"},\"component\":{\"name\":\"HomeHero\",\"options\":{\"backgroundImage\":\"https://cdn.builder.io/api/v1/image/assets%2F6a96e08774184353b3aa88032e406411%2F4f6db6a292c24721bc8c9cc6d457b958?width=2400\",\"wistiaVideoId\":\"en6s1q6p8w\",\"heading\":\"Close the gap between AI spend and AI adoption.\",\"subheading\":\"Pendo captures user behavior across your software and agents, identifies where users struggle, and puts that context to work—so your AI gets smarter in real time and every user gets a better experience.\",\"primaryCtaText\":\"Get a Demo\",\"videoAriaLabel\":\"Pendo Agent Analytics product showcase\",\"secondaryCtaText\":\"Explore the platform\",\"primaryCtaUrl\":\"#\",\"primaryCtaOpenModal\":true},\"isRSC\":null},\"responsiveStyles\":{\"large\":{\"display\":\"flex\",\"flexDirection\":\"column\",\"position\":\"relative\",\"flexShrink\":\"0\",\"boxSizing\":\"border-box\"}}},{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/sdk:Element\",\"@version\":2,\"tagName\":\"div\",\"id\":\"builder-529708efa3054c31815908b7424a00f3\",\"properties\":{\"id\":\"pendoPlatform\"},\"meta\":{\"previousId\":\"builder-c2f5f68df38e40d09a6910b58621bd6c\"},\"children\":[{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/sdk:Element\",\"@version\":2,\"layerName\":\"pendo platform section\",\"id\":\"builder